{"tid":2406610,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"白銀供不應求！！！","createTime":"2021-02-13T10:55:21.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T14:00:15.000Z","uid":391458,"like":3,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"1d44ee1c17231f91f87789db690fda58d5c80d07","tid":2406610,"uid":391458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:55:21.000Z","msg":"前倫敦金銀市場參與者丹尼爾（Daniel） 簡易解釋白銀赤字！！！<br />\n<br />\n2021年白銀供應需艱難。像我們從未見過的赤字耗盡了所有白銀出產。<br />\n<br />\n直接擁有#Silver #Bullion和/或受信任的$ PSLV<br />\n<br />\n詹姆斯&middot;安德森2/13/21<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2021年<br />\n<br />\n礦山供應866Moz<br />\n回收180Moz<br />\n<br />\n總計1,046Moz<br />\n<br />\n工業510Moz<br />\n硬幣和金條257Moz<br />\n珠寶174Moz<br />\n銀器45Moz<br />\n攝影30Moz<br />\nETP 137Moz（截至2月3日）<br />\n<br />\n總計1,153Moz。<br />\n<br />\n簡而言之，僅是二月份，白銀市場已經預見到約100Moz的赤字。到交易所交易產品（ETP）的額外淨流入以及257Moz以上的額外實物投資將決定到年底的赤字程度。<br />\n<br />\n丹尼爾3月2/13/21<br />\n<br />\n來源：<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.silverinstitute.org/global-silver-demand-forecasted-rise-11-percent-2021-reaching-1-025-billion-ounces/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.silverinstitute.org%2Fglobal-silver-demand-forecasted-rise-11-percent-2021-reaching-1-025-billion-ounces%2F&d=kdQtjCisvz5VKkzPdH2zQ%2FrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=e52f1d42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.silverinstitute.org/global-silver-demand-forecasted-rise-11-percent-2021-reaching-1-025-billion-ounces/</a>"},{"pid":"237eee8bccf76b6f872ba1959297080db3563764","tid":2406610,"uid":194166,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:54:40.000Z","msg":"樓主睇好白銀? 有冇咩insight?"},{"pid":"9bc2006e9c630f63ab0ba296734181d6fcabee44","tid":2406610,"uid":177578,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T07:55:46.000Z","msg":"要人生翻盤<br />\n就睇今次<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgm